# Python boundaries

- `core` is pure, typed, deterministic, and unaware of FastAPI or media libraries.
- `services` orchestrate use cases; `adapters` handle formats and external tools.
- Routes validate and translate HTTP only.
- Use immutable domain models and dependency direction toward `core`.
- Never log or persist source document text.
- Add tests with every behavior change.
